title: compose()
brief: Begin composing a new email.
seealso: editor, reply, sent_mail, sendmail_path, send_email
version: 0.07
----

<p>This function will prompt for a recipient &amp; subject, then open your editor to compose a new email.</p>
<p>You can specify the editor to use via the <span class="tt">editor()</span> primitive.</p>
<p>After prompting for confirmation the outgoing mail will then be sent, and a copy written to your configured sent-mail folder.</p>

